Ansible-mongodb
=========

Requirement
-----------

Edit mongodb_version in var/main.yml to install a specific version

Role Variables
--------------

- mongodb_source_key
- mongodb_source_url
- mongodb_verion

mongdb.yaml
-----------

---
- hosts: all
  gather_facts: false
  become: true
  rolse:
  - ansible-mongodb

How to use
----------------

ansible-playbook -i hosts mongodb.yaml
